    {
      "id": "PopularPost339031",
      "post_content": "@tavaritz:  \nActually the rule applied to all non-creature artifacts, even mono artifacts. There were exceptions for artifacts having untap costs (Mana Vault, Basalt Monolith, Time Vault) or specifically doing something when tapped (Mana Vault). Of course it didn't usually didn't matter with mono artifacts, since they needed to tap to activate.  \n  \nEDIT: Just for clarification, the rule of non-creature artifacts not working if tapped existed even during Revised and Fourth Editions, maybe even longer, and at that time, there were no more mono, poly, or continuous artifacts. But as mentioned, Time Vault and Mana Vault and similar had exceptions to still having to pay for untapping.",
      "posted_by": "mtkaim",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost339031\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">@tavaritz:<br/>Actually the rule applied to all non-creature artifacts, even mono artifacts. There were exceptions for artifacts having untap costs (Mana Vault, Basalt Monolith, Time Vault) or specifically doing something when tapped (Mana Vault). Of course it didn't usually didn't matter with mono artifacts, since they needed to tap to activate.<br/><br/>EDIT: Just for clarification, the rule of non-creature artifacts not working if tapped existed even during Revised and Fourth Editions, maybe even longer, and at that time, there were no more mono, poly, or continuous artifacts. But as mentioned, Time Vault and Mana Vault and similar had exceptions to still having to pay for untapping.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '339031'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy100809\">mtkaim</span>\r\n                                (9/16/2013 3:26:23 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainCo